	<h1 class="title">看看现在，很难相信这家麦当劳曾是全城最难看的房子</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1329/small/1329.jpg?1418779602" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">胡莹 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-06-09 13:37:20 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/10577/medium/10577.jpg?1436647430" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="10577" data-title="《看看现在，很难相信这家麦当劳曾是全城最难看的房子》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/10577/medium/10577.jpg?1436647430" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/10577.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
